situation where here

00:34:49.690 --> 00:34:52.680
in the United States
we did not have copies

00:34:52.680 --> 00:34:55.040
of our own newspapers.

00:34:55.040 --> 00:34:56.340
&gt;&gt; Carla Hayden: That's right.

00:34:56.340 --> 00:34:57.640
&gt;&gt; David Ferriero: Because
the microfilm was --

00:34:57.640 --> 00:35:02.650
and the microfilm is so poorly
created and disintegrated

00:35:02.650 --> 00:35:05.250
in some cases but
there was no --

00:35:05.250 --> 00:35:08.190
in lots of reels
no quality control.

00:35:08.190 --> 00:35:12.660
