and the worst thing was

00:35:12.660 --> 00:35:19.690
that many of the -- The New York
Herald was the first, I believe,

00:35:19.690 --> 00:35:21.850
newspaper to introduce color

00:35:21.850 --> 00:35:26.480
into the comics on
Sunday editions.

00:35:26.480 --> 00:35:29.310
